channel.description:

item.title: Wth?
item.dc:creator: @Graham Graham
item.description:
@Graham wrote:

Search for the error:

int cannot be dereferenced

It means your trying to use an int type as a class, whereas it is not (it is a primitive variable).

Check out this:

http://forum.java.sun.com/thread.jspa?threadID=500376&messageID=2365065

Read full topic
